sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
Generate random user data and output all data to variables that can be used to create User and Location records.

Inputs
  • Gender
  • Nationality
Outputs
  • Username
  • First name
  • Last name
  • Email
  • Street
  • City
  • State
  • Postal code
  • Latitude
  • Longitude
  • Time zone offset
  • Time zone description
  • Password
  • Date of birth
  • Phone
  • Mobile
  • Nationality
  • Seed
